# KairOS engine — vault content at repo root must never be tracked.
# Patterns are anchored (leading /) so engine paths like skills/goals/ stay visible to git.

/daily/
/inbox/
/north-star/
/goals/
/projects/
/reference/
/council/
/archive/

/inbox.md
/next-actions.md
/waiting-for.md
/someday-maybe.md
/profile.md
/habits.md

# Example and placeholder files still ship
!*.example.md
!.gitkeep

# Test harness scratch dirs
/test/tmp/

# GSD / local dev tooling (not part of the shipped engine)
.gsd-id
gsd-install-state.json
gsd-migration-journal/
.bg-shell/
.claude/gsd-install-state.json
